package system.services.diag

// The diag FC process: the DoIP socket server (DoipServer) + the UDS router
// (UdsRouter). DiagTester is probe-only (NOT a composition member). Mirrors com
// (the runnable + its TIPC peer in one process).
composition Diag {
    prototype DoipServer doip_server
    prototype UdsRouter  uds_router
}
